==Beskrivning==

The '''Arch MeshToShape''' tool converts a selected [[Mesh|Mesh]] ([[Mesh_Feature|Mesh Feature]]) object into a [[Shape|Shape]] ([[Part_Feature|Part Feature]]) object.

This tool is optimized for objects with flat faces (no curves). The corresponding tool [[File:Part_ShapeFromMesh.svg|16px]] [[Part_ShapeFromMesh|Part ShapeFromMesh]] might be more suited for objects that contain curved surfaces.

